    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MegaRacer QuantumRush - 终极开放世界赛车体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MegaRacer QuantumRush</strong> 为VR竞速游戏设定了新的标准，提供沉浸式的开放世界卡丁车竞速体验。玩家将在巨大的未来都市 <strong>Mega City</strong> 中驾驶独特的卡丁车，与可爱的动画角色一起穿越多种游戏模式。这款游戏旨在满足从初学者到资深玩家的不同水平，为每位玩家提供丰富多彩的游戏内容。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多种游戏模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/7e4ce710d93b3f012228573ffd950677.poster.avif?t=1755754073\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/7e4ce710d93b3f012228573ffd950677.webm?t=1755754073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/7e4ce710d93b3f012228573ffd950677.mp4?t=1755754073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MegaRacer QuantumRush</strong> 带来的不仅仅是普通的竞速游戏体验，还包括以下多种模式，带来持续的新鲜感：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >街道竞速：在 <strong>Mega City</strong> 的都市街道中飞驰，体验高速与灵活操作的快感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >障碍竞速：充满战略性的挑战模式，需要克服复杂的障碍夺取胜利。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >皇冠争夺战：在限时内获取皇冠并防守到底，才能赢得胜利。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >足球模式：结合竞速与足球的独特玩法，驾驶卡丁车控球进球，展现团队合作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他单人及多人模式：在 <strong>Mega City</strong> 探索10种以上别具特色的模式与特别事件，等你挑战！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>兼具VR沉浸感与PC平台舒适性的体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/1c2bb671764425c5797af963cae27564.poster.avif?t=1755754073\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/1c2bb671764425c5797af963cae27564.webm?t=1755754073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/1c2bb671764425c5797af963cae27564.mp4?t=1755754073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MegaRacer QuantumRush</strong> 同时支持PC与VR平台，即使长时间游玩也能保持舒适体验。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高级视角处理：采用特别设计的VR摄像头与机制，最大程度减少晕动症，提供清爽的游戏体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作方式自由切换：无论是沉浸式的方向盘操作，还是使用摇杆与键盘，都可自由切换，畅游 <strong>Mega City</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持多种输入设备：键盘、鼠标、手柄与VR控制器皆可使用，依照玩家习惯无缝切换。<br>即使没有VR设备，在PC平台也能享受流畅直观的操作与视觉体验，完整体验游戏乐趣。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >卡丁车与角色自定义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/0b6a51fbbbd64a88b234fac3f179a5a6.avif?t=1755754073\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras_big/0b6a51fbbbd64a88b234fac3f179a5a6.avif?t=1755754073 width=800 height=162 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>MegaRacer QuantumRush</strong> 中，玩家可自由定制自己的卡丁车与角色。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡丁车自定义：可选择颜色、零件与各种设计，打造专属座驾。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色装扮：可爱的角色可更换特殊服饰与装备，展现你的个性风格。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人人都能享受的赛车体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/70d43922f7adbdd4a13fe7239c4a0537.poster.avif?t=1755754073\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/70d43922f7adbdd4a13fe7239c4a0537.webm?t=1755754073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是新手还是老司机，<strong>MegaRacer QuantumRush</strong> 都提供适合每位玩家的游戏体验。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样竞速体验：在热闹的多人竞速中争夺第一，或独自探索 <strong>Mega City</strong>，享受解谜、时间挑战、漂移赛等丰富内容！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与社区共创未来</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/e9ac406278d94b326cebd6acf17139d5.avif?t=1755754073\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras_big/e9ac406278d94b326cebd6acf17139d5.avif?t=1755754073 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MegaRacer QuantumRush</strong> 致力于与玩家社区紧密合作，不断优化游戏体验。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定期内容更新将新增赛道、模式与自定义选项。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过Beta测试与问卷调查，收集反馈，持续改善游戏品质。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在 Mega City 的世界中，开启属于你的竞速旅程！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras/b648813032a04afc9e5e4df4cf61ec4c.avif?t=1755754073\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104610/extras_big/b648813032a04afc9e5e4df4cf61ec4c.avif?t=1755754073 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在速度与策略交织的比赛中，成为终极赛车手吧。穿梭于 <strong>Mega City</strong> 的街头巷尾，挑战各种模式，打造属于你的竞速风格。<strong>MegaRacer QuantumRush</strong> 为所有平台的玩家带来前所未有的休闲竞速体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
